  - Invocation=The Dispeller of Sin
Commentary: |
  \‘The teaching of Amida and his Pure Land is found throughout the Nô’
  (Beatrice Lane Suzuki: Nôgaku. p. 40).
---
Ceaselessly I have performed the ritual of the Holy Name that clears all
sin away.
